User/Group Profile
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
This class is used to generate entity profile

    data format: {
        ID        : "EntityID",        // entity ID
        type      : "visa",            // "bulletin", ...
        data      : "{JSON}",          // data = json_encode(info)
        signature : "{BASE64_ENCODE}"  // signature = sign(data, SK);
    }
